title: The Pac-12 Owns Entertainment - Week 4, Recapped
description:
Two things you will learn on this episode:
1. Never watch Georgia! 
2. Always watch the Pac-12!
Other things you will heard discussed on this episode!
- The delightful weirdness of UCLA-Washington State
- Pitt saved its only good idea for an opponent who might not even be accredited
- The worst Arkansas team to ever be televised
- Finally, communism accomplishes something
